Commentary Text: Axar to Karthik, out Lbw!! For the second time today, Axar comes roaring back next ball after conceding a boundary previous delivery. Went for the fastish slider, attacking the stumps and Karthik had no time to unleash his reverse sweep. Late on the shot and hit on the pad right in front of the sticks. Axar knew straightaway and the ump also raised his finger pretty quickly. Karthik gambled with the review but once he missed it, he was going to be in trouble. Three Reds! Big dent for KKR. Karthik lbw b Axar 14(10) [4s-1 6s-1]
